 Leon would like that too.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Yay~! Thanks, Chii-chan.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"And thanks for being good during the walk, Leon. Let's go again sometime.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Fufu, Leon looks so happy.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"I want to keep playing with you guys, but it's getting late.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Yeah, it'll be dark soon. You should probably go home.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"But-","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"If you don't go quickly, the ghosts will come out, Kao-chan.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Ghosts?! Don't say that~! I'll be too scared to move.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Fufu, ghosts are pretty unrealistic anyway, scientifically speaking. I think it's mostly just people mistaking what they see. There's probably no such thing as ghosts.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Probably...? But doesn't that mean they also could be real...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"What should I do...? I'm a bit scared now...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":321,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Kao-chan... I guess there's only one solution. Leon and I will walk you home.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"I was the one that mentioned ghosts, after all.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"You would do that?! Oh, but then you would have to walk back home alone, Chii-chan.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"I have Leon, so I'll be fine. Now, let's get going before it's too dark.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Okay...! Thanks, Chii-chan, and you too, Leon.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Fufu, it seems like Leon loves being around you anyway.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Really? I'm glad~. Let's play again sometime, Leon.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"... Huh? What's with the barking? What's wrong?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Leon's barking toward that empty lot over there... Is there something there? Or... someone...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Is it a gh-ghost?! What should we do?! There might be a ghost!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"I-it's fine. There's no such thing as ghosts... I'm sure it's nothing.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"ev100-ep1-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"But why bark at nothing...?","tention":0